abstract.p: To provide a polymerizable composition and a polymerized product of the polymerizable composition which has excellent wettability to various base materials such as an organic base material, an inorganic base material and a base material made of an organic-inorganic composite material having a wide range of polarity from low to high polarity, high transparency and curability and can provide a cured product having excellent water resistance when cured, and provide various types of molding using these.SOLUTION: There is provided a polymerizable composition comprising an N-substituted (meth) acrylamide represented by the general formula [1]. (wherein, R1 represents a hydrogen atom or a methyl group, one of R2 and R3 represents a chain hydrocarbon group having 6 or more carbon atoms or a ring hydrocarbon group having 6 or more carbon atoms and the other represents a hydrogen atom, a chain hydrocarbon group having 1 or more carbon atoms or a ring hydrocarbon group having 3 or more carbon atoms and R2 and R3 may form a 6- or more-membered saturated ring with a nitrogen atom supporting them.)
